    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>The Mixer</strong> you will create your own music and then fight to its rhythm. Your arsenal is made up of 5 different music loops and you need to mix-and-match them to define your combat style as well as create the dominant soundtrack of the game. Choose a fast melody for a rapid attack pattern, or pick a slow one to have stronger individual hits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the beat mechanics and figure out the most powerful combinations of items and music to overcome a series of hand-crafted challenges, filled with waves of enemies and a unique boss fight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield your beat and enter the fracturing mind of a fantasy bard to conquer his rhythmic subconscious! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/c944478b85c3a074150b61b24984e102.webp?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/1b2f211f298e6e73111e94a34895ee84.avif?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soundboard mechanic that allows players to build their own soundtrack from a set of loops (much akin to how a sample machine works). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/9c5ccaf7415c10bf683d5273fad5fc53.webp?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/1a396f0db6258b97f5633a949cd4f0ec.poster.avif?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/1a396f0db6258b97f5633a949cd4f0ec.webm?t=1771945949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique take on rhythm-based combat that varies greatly depending on what kind of track you build. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/27ee302a8168889ac1eccbd6d71655cb.webp?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/e9f40b30db9e3e3f010e9ec5b385bc9b.avif?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tried and true dungeon crawling where you unlock new music loops and receive resources for permanent character upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/6c35396e6922e583bbfda9c9ec44544a.avif?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/451edfd2c9f7b4cd134a10be63ef5599.avif?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=136 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167400/extras/45f1a9a4909c3a4f7834a0821e9e3074.avif?t=1771945949\" width=600 height=136 /></span></p>",
